Full-Stack Fitness Tracker MVP
A streamlined web application for logging workouts and meals, tracking calories, and viewing simple health insights. Built with React, Node.js, and MongoDB.
Project Overview
This MVP empowers users to:
- Log workouts with activity type, duration, and calories
- Track meals with nutritional details
- View historical data and simple stats
- Register and log in securely with JWT authentication
The application is built with modular architecture and a focus on usability, allowing for clear separation between frontend and backend responsibilities.
Tech Stack
Frontend:
- React with React Router
- styled-components
Backend:
- Node.js + Express
- MongoDB + Mongoose
- Authentication via JWT
- Validation with express-validator
- Middleware: helmet, morgan, cors
