Getting Started
1. Backend Setup
cd backend
npm install
touch .env


.env file:
PORT=5000
MONGO_URI=mongodb://localhost/fitness_tracker
JWT_SECRET=yourSecretKey


Run the server:
npm run dev


2. Frontend Setup
cd ../frontend
npm install
npm start


Frontend runs on http://localhost:3000. Backend runs on http://localhost:5000.
API Overview
Auth:
- POST /api/auth/register – create user
- POST /api/auth/login – returns JWT
Exercise:
- GET /api/exercise – all workouts
- POST /api/exercise – add workout
Nutrition:
- GET /api/nutrition – all meals
- POST /api/nutrition – add meal
